  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the cognitive inhibition deficit among depressed
      older suicide attempters compared to depressed older suicide non-attempters.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The main objective consists in examining the association between cognitive inhibition and
      suicide attempt in depressed older adults (&gt; 65 year old).
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
